#

Maple Pecan Waffles

25 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastComfort FoodEasy

Description

Fluffy waffles topped with crunchy pecans and a drizzle of maple syrup for a perfect breakfast treat.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 ½ cups
  • baking powder: 2 teaspoons
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: ½ teaspoon
  • milk: 1 cup
  • egg: 1 large
  • unsalted butter: ⅓ cup
  • chopped pecans: ½ cup
  • maple syrup: for serving
